'''Melchior Ndadaye''' (* 28.03.1953, [[Marama]], [[Uburundi]] — † 21.10.1993, [[Bujumbura]], Uburundi), umukuru w'igihugu ca [[Uburundi]] (1993), ihirikwa ry’amaraso ryakorewe Ndadaye ryateje ubwiyongere bw’ihohoterwa rya politiki hagati y’amoko yombi, ritangira intambara y’abenegihugu yo mu Burundi, izakomeza kugeza mu 2005 hamwe n’amatora ya [[Pierre Nkurunziza]].
